p:
The proximate composition of the fruit has been reported. He et al. reported that no fat was present in the flesh while ten different fatty acids were identified in the seed oil with a total unsaturated fatty acid content of 52.7%. Vitamins A, C, D and K were reported present. Specifically, the fruit was reported to contain a large amount of vitamin C making it an important source of the vitamin (
 He et al., 2016; 
 Nkwocha et al., 2014a).
